title: 85 South Live Variety Show @ Smith's Olde Bar | #002
itunes:title: 85 South Live Variety Show @ Smith's Olde Bar | #002
description:
The 85 SouthShow Live Variety Show returns to Smith's Olde Bar in Atlanta for a night to remember! Freestyles and jokes the super talented group had the packed house cracking up all night! With special guests Navv Greene, Tyler Chronicles, ZooMan Miller, Fatt Man Deezy, artist 7am and an unexpected performance from the OG BoneCrusher there was never a dull moment! We hope you enjoy listening to it as much as we enjoyed producing it. #ThisPodcastIsFor
